
The moderator's journey starts from a simple site - drawaria.online/getserverstate

          drawaria.online/getserverstate


Site loads a quick rooms list, where moderators can see:

- Rooms
- Rooms canvas
- Rooms description
- Players in rooms
- Players hash
- Players country

Also in getserverstate they can do the same as moderators in other platform


- Message to player from moderator (The message will be seen for him only)
- Ban
- Kick

This site was made just to see rooms quickly.

------------------------------------------------- MOD MENU ------------------------------------------------

Basically lets explain how moderators can do a lot of stuff with players, when in getserverstate they can do only three actions

https://drawaria.online/modpanel?server=3&room=(Room id)&player=(id of player)&openmenu=(1 or 0)

The menu can be opened by changing url data or Ctrl + Shift + click on a player

by changing openmenu= to 0 youre just seeing the room, without moderator tools (Like a snapshot)
by changing openmenu= to 1 youre you can see room and moderator tools

In moderators tools by RCON they can:

1. /rcon/kickplayer/{roomId}/{playerId}/{reason}  // kick
2. /rcon/banplayer/{ip}/{type}/{reason}/{time}/{accountId}/{snapshotId}/{roomId}/{playerId} // ban
3. /rcon/resetname/{roomId}/{playerId} // reset name of player
4. /rcon/resetavatar/{roomId}/{playerId} // reset avatar
5. /rcon/clearcanvas/{roomId} // clear canvas
6. /rcon/rollbackcanvas/{roomId} // rollback canvas
7. /rcon/clearplaylist/{roomId} // clearplaylist (useless)
8. /rcon/resetname/{roomId} // reset description room
9. /rcon/startmatch/{roomId} // start match
10. /rcon/msg/{message}/{roomId}/{playerId} // message to player from Moderator: face (Write id if you want send this to player, or dont write the player id, in result you will send a moderator message to everyone in room)
11. /rcon/msg/rules:2/{roomId}/{playerId} // send rules in room to player or to whole room
12. /rcon/snapshot/{roomId}?retjson=1 // save room data (or else snapshot creation)
13. /rcon/snapshot/{roomId}/{playerId}/ban/ // create snapshot for a ban
14. /rcon/snapshotlist/{roomId} // see snapshots by room uuid
15. /rcon/getfpid/{roomId}/{playerId} // fingerprint of player in room (dont know what is this)


